                        "block": "<p>When an account is created, you'll be able to quickly access your complete order history and save payment and shipping address information, which makes placing additional orders quicker and easier.</p><p>Establishing an account also gives you access to BodySpace, an online social community filled with people who are working hard to build a healthier body and mind. On BodySpace, you can set a goal, establish a plan to achieve it, track your progress towards it, and find the motivation needed to smash that goal to pieces. Members can also upload progress photos, rate their favorite supplements, write a blog, track body measurements, and share success stories with friends.</p><p>You can easily create a profile on the <a href='profile/signup'>Account Registration page</a>.</p>"
