                        "block": "<p>Having friends with similar aspirations can make a big difference when it comes to accomplishing your own health and fitness goals.</p><h2>Adding Friends:</h2><p>You can add someone as a friend by going to the ‘Member Search' section of BodySpace.</p><h2>Removing Friends</h2><p>You can remove friends by logging in and going to your friends page. From there you can click on the friend button to remove a user from your friends list.</p>"
